On a last minute call from creative director and model @badaraofficial as he was boarding a plane from Paris to New York to be the on this shoot, he shared his ideas on what he planned to accomplish here. By the time he boarded I had a sense this was going to be very special, as we got together in the studio we created a whole campaign for the lovely Mauren who had put her heart, soul and money to bring her dream to reality. With such great taste, she is was able to create an unique experience for her customers.  @wantmaure just opened at the Oculus station on the WTC last week. I hope you enjoy these images and if you are in NY go visit her beautiful store.

#blackhistorymonth #creativity #newtorkcity #artwork #blackisbeautiful #nyc #photography

Vintage Portraits, Los Angeles 
 
From a time before digital, instead of the laptop, the darkroom,
 
The smell of acetic acid and the magic of the wet paper became a photo right before my eyes 

Timeless images found going through my now, digitalized arquives. 

Models, lovers, dancers, friends, were my subjects as I was taking my first footsteps into the world of image-making.
 
I love the poetry of a heroic moment,
I use powerful expression, emotion, shape, lighting, and form to sculpt an image and help to tell the hidden stories within.
I approach life and career with a lust for “a knowing of” what makes my subjects tick.

Let’s figure out a way to work together.

RVN: Designs infused with New York DNA

Founded in 2012 RVN is a brand that beautifully weaves the sensibility of its lead designer and founder Ted Kim, with the dynamic spirit of New York City. Together, we immersed ourselves in the vibrant streets of downtown Manhattan, utilizing the ever-iconic World Trade Center and an industrial rooftop in the heart of Brooklyn as our backdrop where we captured the essence of RVN in a visually stunning lookbook and high-concept editorial shoot.

Talent: Cara Fravel @carafravel, Astrid Voss @astridv0ss, 
Sonia Okumu @soniaookumu
Creative Director: Ted Kim @rvnnyc
Photographer: Alex Korolkovas @korolkovas 
Production: Joe Lombardo @iamjoelombardo 
Makeup: Karla Hirkaler @karlahirkaler
Hair: Sofia Garcia
Stylist: Stephanie W @s.tephaniewenger
Photo Assistant: Nano Leon @nanoleonstudio
Videographer: Lucas Asensi @lucasasensi
Vegan Catering: Mariana Tamiozzy @marianatamiozzy
